
=========*

HOW TO SOLVE WIZARD AND THE PRINCESS

=========*

[ WARNING !!! THIS SHOWS HOW TO WIN
   STEP BY STEP.  THESE ARE NOT HINTS ]

   D E S E R T
  -- - - - - --

FROM THE VILLAGE:

N, E, E, E, E, N, E, N, W

GET ROCK--(THIS ONE IS SAFE TO GET)

N, W, N, W, N, W, N

(YOU ARE NOW BACK AT SNAKE)

THROW ROCK, N, DRINK WATER, E,
GET STICK (YOU WILL NEED THE STICK TO
           WARD OFF THE SNAKES THAT
           PERIODICALLY APPEAR.  TYPE
           THROW STICK AND SNAKE WILL
           GO AWAY.)

W, N, THROW STICK, LOOK HOLE, GET NOTE,
N, W, LIFT ROCK (THE KING WILL GIVE YOU
                 THE MAGIC WORD 'HISS')
N, GET NOTE, E, GET LOCKET, E, E, S, W,

W, LOOK HOLE, GET CRACKER,

 E, N, N, W, N, W, N (YOU ARE NOW AT
                      THE CHASM)


  A F T E R  T H E  C H A S M 
 -- - - - -- ----- -- - - - --

SAY HOCUS, N, GO HOUSE, GET APPLE, W, N

(YOU WILL SEE A LITTLE GNOME, TYPE
 'LOOK GNOME'.  HE WILL GRAB SOME OF
 YOUR STUFF, THIS IS NORMAL.)

N, E, SAY HISS, GO CREVICE, S, S, S,
GET BREAD, GET LOCKET, GET CRACKER,
UNLOCK DOOR, OPEN DOOR, GO DOOR, U,
GO HOLE, N, E, S, GIVE CRACKER,

GET VIAL, N, W, S, W, W, THROW BREAD,
N, GET ROPE, GO BOAT, USE BLANKET 


 A T  S E A  O N  A  B O A T
-- - -- - - -- -- - -- - - --

N, N, DRINK WATER, N, E, E, E, GO BEACH


  T H E  I S L A N D ! !
--- - -- - - - - - - - --

N, N, E, GET ANCHOR, W, TIE ROPE,
TO ANCHOR, THROW ANCHOR, UP, GET SHOVEL

DOWN, S, S, DIG X, LOOK TREASURE

(A PIRATE WILL JUMP OUT, GRAB THE CHEST
 AND LEAVE, THIS IS O.K.)

E, N, W, GO CAVE, OPEN CHEST,
LOOK CHEST, GET HARP

 N, E, N, DRINK VIAL, FLY NORTH


  T H E  2ND C O N T I N E N T
 -- - -  --- - - - - - - - - --

 N, GET RING, N, W, FOLLOW RAINBOW,
 GET COIN, N, SAY LUCY, W, W, N,
 GO CAVE

 GET ALL, N, S, W, PLAY HARP (THE GIANT
                             WILL RUN
                             OFF WITH
                             IT.)

N, N, BUY HORN, N, N, BLOW HORN (BRIDGE
                                LOWERS)

NORTH


    C  A  S  T  L  E
------------------------

U, E, OPEN CLOSET, LOOK CLOSET,
 GET SHOES, LOOK SHOES, W, D, W, W,

LOOK THRONE  (AT THIS POINT YOU WILL
              'HEAR AN EVIL LAUGH' AND
              ARE 'ZAPPED' TO ANOTHER
              PLACE.)
THROW APPLE  (BOAR EATS IT)


N, E, LOOK CABINET ( YOU WILL BE ZAPPED
                     AGAIN.)

PICK LOCK, WITH KNIFE, OPEN DOOR,

E, U, D, U, WEAR RING,

 RUB RING  (YOU JUST ATE THE WIZARD!
            ALL OF HIS MAGIC IS GONE
            ... BURP !)

D, E, KISS FROG, WEAR SHOES, SAY WHOOSH


   B A C K  I N  T H E  D E S E R T 
 --- - - -  ---  -----  - - - - - ---

TALK, .....  YOU  WON !!!!!!!!!

        YOU HAVE SOLVED .........

       WIZARD AND THE PRINCESS!!!


WRITTEN BY SLIMY LOUIE

=========*

